@startuml
' 径向间隙中的倒流/潜流 + 间隙旋涡
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontName "PingFang SC"
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #FDECEC
  BorderColor    #C0392B
  FontColor      #1A1A1A
  RoundCorner    10
}
skinparam ArrowColor #C0392B
skinparam ArrowFontSize 12

left to right direction

rectangle "叶盆\n(压力面·高压)" as pressure
rectangle "叶背\n(吸力面·低压)" as suction

pressure --> suction : 径向间隙潜流\n(高压→低压倒流)
pressure --> "间隙旋涡" : 端壁运动时\n(端壁相对叶片移动)

note bottom of suction
  二次流损失来源之一:
  径向间隙中的倒流 / 潜流
  + 间隙旋涡
  一般限制在叶片高度的 0.5% ~ 1%
end note

@enduml
